{"content":"    \r\n    <h1 id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager\">\r\n      <span class=\"lang-csharp\">BufferManager</span>\r\n        Class\r\n    </h1>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    <nav id=\"center-doc-outline\" class=\"doc-outline\" ms.cmpgrp=\"intopic toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"On page navigation\">\r\n      <h3>In this Article</h3>\r\n    </nav><div class=\"summary\">\r\n    \t<p>Many <!-- BEGIN INCLUDE: Include content from &quot;~/add/includes/indigo1-md.md&quot; -->Windows Communication Foundation (WCF)<!--END INCLUDE --> features require the use of buffers, which are expensive to create and destroy. You can use the BufferManager class to manage a buffer pool. The pool and its buffers are created when you instantiate this class and destroyed when the buffer pool is reclaimed by garbage collection. Every time you need to use a buffer, you take one from the pool, use it, and return it to the pool when done. This process is much faster than creating and destroying a buffer every time you need to use one.</p>\n\r\n    </div><h2>Syntax</h2>\r\n    \r\n    \t<h3>Declaration</h3>\r\n    \t<pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public abstract class BufferManager</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    <h3>Inheritance Hierarchy</h3>\r\n    <ul class=\"inheritance\">\r\n        <li class=\"l0\">\r\n          <div class=\"lang-csharp\">\r\n            <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.object\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">System.Object</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </li>\r\n      <li class=\"l1\">\r\n        <div class=\"xref\">\r\n          <div class=\"lang-csharp\">BufferManager</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    \r\n      <div class=\"referencebox inheritedMembers\">\r\n        <h3>Inherited Members</h3>\r\n        <h4></h4>\r\n          <div class=\"lang-csharp\">\r\n            <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.object#System_Object_Equals_System_Object_\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Equals(Object)</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n          , \r\n          <div class=\"lang-csharp\">\r\n            <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.object#System_Object_Equals_System_Object_System_Object_\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Equals(Object,Object)</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n          , \r\n          <div class=\"lang-csharp\">\r\n            <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.object#System_Object_GetHashCode\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">GetHashCode()</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n          , \r\n          <div class=\"lang-csharp\">\r\n            <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.object#System_Object_GetType\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">GetType()</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n          , \r\n          <div class=\"lang-csharp\">\r\n            <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.object#System_Object_MemberwiseClone\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">MemberwiseClone()</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n          , \r\n          <div class=\"lang-csharp\">\r\n            <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.object#System_Object_ReferenceEquals_System_Object_System_Object_\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ReferenceEquals(Object,Object)</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n          , \r\n          <div class=\"lang-csharp\">\r\n            <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.object#System_Object_ToString\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ToString()</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n          \r\n      </div>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n      <h2>Remarks</h2>\r\n      <p>This class is commonly used while implementing custom encoders or custom transport channels.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    <h2>Constructors\r\n     summary</h2>\r\n    \r\n    <table class=\"nameValue\">\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager__ctor\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">BufferManager()</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Initializes a new instance of the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.servicemodel.channels.buffermanager\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">BufferManager</a> class.</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </table>\r\n    <h2>Methods\r\n     summary</h2>\r\n    \r\n    <table class=\"nameValue\">\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_Clear\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">Clear()</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Releases the buffers currently cached in the manager.</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_CreateBufferManager_System_Int64_System_Int32_\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">CreateBufferManager(Int64,Int32)</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Creates a new BufferManager with a specified maximum buffer pool size and a maximum size for each individual buffer in the pool.</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_ReturnBuffer_System_Byte___\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">ReturnBuffer(Byte[])</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Returns a buffer to the pool.</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_TakeBuffer_System_Int32_\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">TakeBuffer(Int32)</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Gets a buffer of at least the specified size from the pool.</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </table>\r\n    <section class=\"memberGroup\">\r\n      <header class=\"header enable-platform-filter\" id=\"constructors\">\r\n        <h2>Constructors\r\n    </h2>\r\n      </header>\r\n    \r\n      <ul class=\"list-clean enable-platform-filter\">\r\n    \r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager__ctor\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager__ctor_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">BufferManager()</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Initializes a new instance of the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.servicemodel.channels.buffermanager\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">BufferManager</a> class.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">protected BufferManager ();</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Remarks</h4>\r\n            <p>Because this constructor is <code>protected</code>, you can only call it from a derived class.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n    </section><section class=\"memberGroup\">\r\n      <header class=\"header enable-platform-filter\" id=\"methods\">\r\n        <h2>Methods\r\n    </h2>\r\n      </header>\r\n    \r\n      <ul class=\"list-clean enable-platform-filter\">\r\n    \r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_Clear\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_Clear_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">Clear()</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Releases the buffers currently cached in the manager.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public abstract void Clear ();</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_CreateBufferManager_System_Int64_System_Int32_\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_CreateBufferManager_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">CreateBufferManager(Int64,Int32)</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Creates a new BufferManager with a specified maximum buffer pool size and a maximum size for each individual buffer in the pool.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public static System.ServiceModel.Channels.BufferManager CreateBufferManager (long maxBufferPoolSize, int maxBufferSize);</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Parameters</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <dl>\r\n                  <dt>maxBufferPoolSize</dt>\r\n                  <dd>\r\n                    <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.int64\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Int64</a></div>\r\n                  </dd>\r\n                  </dl>\r\n                  <p>The maximum size of the pool.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <dl>\r\n                  <dt>maxBufferSize</dt>\r\n                  <dd>\r\n                    <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.int32\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Int32</a></div>\r\n                  </dd>\r\n                  </dl>\r\n                  <p>The maximum size of an individual buffer.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n              <h4>Returns</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.servicemodel.channels.buffermanager\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">BufferManager</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p>Returns a <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.servicemodel.channels.buffermanager\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">BufferManager</a> object with the specified parameters.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Exceptions</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.insufficientmemoryexception\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">InsufficientMemoryException</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"alert NOTE\"><br> In the <a href=\"http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=247912\" data-linktype=\"external\">.NET for Windows Store apps</a> or the <a href=\"../Topic/Cross-Platform%20Development%20with%20the%20Portable%20Class%20Library.md\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Portable Class Library</a>, catch the base class exception, <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.outofmemoryexception\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">OutOfMemoryException</a>, instead.<br>\n</div>  \n\n<p> There was insufficient memory to create the requested buffer pool.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.argumentoutofrangeexception\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ArgumentOutOfRangeException</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p><code>maxBufferPoolSize</code> or <code>maxBufferSize</code> was less than zero.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Remarks</h4>\r\n            <p>This method creates a new buffer pool with as many buffers as can be created.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_ReturnBuffer_System_Byte___\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_ReturnBuffer_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">ReturnBuffer(Byte[])</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Returns a buffer to the pool.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public abstract void ReturnBuffer (byte[] buffer);</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Parameters</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <dl>\r\n                  <dt>buffer</dt>\r\n                  <dd>\r\n                    <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.byte\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Byte</a>[]</div>\r\n                  </dd>\r\n                  </dl>\r\n                  <p>A reference to the buffer being returned.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Exceptions</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.argumentnullexception\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ArgumentNullException</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p><code>buffer</code> reference cannot be <code>null</code>.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.argumentexception\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ArgumentException</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p>Length of <code>buffer</code> does not match the pool&#39;s buffer length property.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Remarks</h4>\r\n            <p>The buffer is returned to the pool and is available for re-use.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_TakeBuffer_System_Int32_\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ServiceModel_Channels_BufferManager_TakeBuffer_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">TakeBuffer(Int32)</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Gets a buffer of at least the specified size from the pool.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public abstract byte[] TakeBuffer (int bufferSize);</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Parameters</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <dl>\r\n                  <dt>bufferSize</dt>\r\n                  <dd>\r\n                    <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.int32\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Int32</a></div>\r\n                  </dd>\r\n                  </dl>\r\n                  <p>The size, in bytes, of the requested buffer.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n              <h4>Returns</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.byte\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Byte</a>[]</div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p>A byte array that is the requested size of the buffer.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Exceptions</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.argumentoutofrangeexception\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ArgumentOutOfRangeException</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p><code>bufferSize</code> cannot be less than zero.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Remarks</h4>\r\n            <p>If successful, the system returns a byte array buffer of at least the requested size.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n    </section>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n","outputRootRelativePath":"./","pageMetadata":"<meta name=\"breadcrumb_path\" content=\"breadcrumb/toc.json\">\r\n<meta name=\"search.ms_sitename\" content=\"Docs\">\r\n<meta name=\"search.ms_docsetname\" content=\"fulldocset\">\r\n<meta name=\"locale\" content=\"en-us\">\r\n<meta name=\"site_name\" content=\"Docs\">\r\n<meta name=\"search.ms_product\" content=\"MSDN\">\r\n<meta name=\"depot_name\" content=\"MSDN.fulldocset\">\r\n<meta name=\"ref_skeleton_gitcommit\" content=\"https://github.com/TianqiZhang/ECMA2YamlTestRepo2/blob/501959ac03e19ac52a27aa4c6bbeb980f8b11c8c/fulldocset/System.ServiceModel.Channels.BufferManager.yml\">\r\n<meta name=\"original_ref_skeleton_git_url\" content=\"https://github.com/TianqiZhang/ECMA2YamlTestRepo2/blob/master/fulldocset/System.ServiceModel.Channels.BufferManager.yml\">\r\n<meta name=\"APIName\" content=\"System.ServiceModel.Channels.BufferManager\">\r\n<meta name=\"APIName\" content=\"System.ServiceModel.Channels.BufferManager..ctor\">\r\n<meta name=\"APIName\" content=\"System.ServiceModel.Channels.BufferManager.Clear\">\r\n<meta name=\"APIName\" content=\"System.ServiceModel.Channels.BufferManager.CreateBufferManager\">